{"tid":1884657,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[面對現實]業主逆市加租逾12％　旺角CAFE被迫結業","createTime":"2020-02-17T17:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T16:32:54.000Z","uid":141026,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"520e64a31fafe8235b2c5021abbc23bf357d419f","tid":1884657,"uid":141026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T17:48:00.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情對食肆生意帶來衝擊。除了生意額大減外，有店舖更面對逆市加租情況，被迫而結業。<br />\n<br />\n位於旺角的「街坊CAF&Eacute;」負責人陳先生指，近一年內生意持續虧損，加上租約3月底完結，業主卻要求加租逾兩萬元，加幅高達12％至16%。他稱，當時租此舖時已是頂位價，未想到業主更會逆市加租，實在無法負擔，故只能計劃下月結業。<br />\n<br />\n問及港府將對食店提供津貼，能否改變他停業的念頭。他坦言「的確可以為領取津貼而捱幾個月貴租」，但由於措施尚未有發放細節，質疑這樣等待的意義不大。他又認為，港府單靠派錢並不能解決所有問題，「津貼只維持食店一至二個月的經營，加上不少店舖已縮減人手，措施未能幫助被裁的員工。」<br />\n<br />\n租金GOGOGO<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2565872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2565872&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbDRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=f4953dac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2565872</a>"},{"pid":"e758ce7de51ae6aa1a9d27b33686faaf375d6837","tid":1884657,"uid":310534,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T18:10:45.000Z","msg":"咩原因會令業主逆市加租？"},{"pid":"979c1434b50c09b512dc69814fa26266a13bb62e","tid":1884657,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T18:15:00.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbDRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=3261342f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"4dc5e3435ac06956456e7fb1bcb70ea7ce2b53d0","tid":1884657,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote